Client details: Cynthia Gibson, born 10/21/1975, SSN 400-33-0003, phone 502-921-6076. She resides at 1105 N Buckman St, Apt A2, Shepherdsville, KY 40165. The case involves PIP through State Farm, with Claim # 4720852C0317 and reference 1787K940X. The case is associated with Bullitt County Police Department, Report # 25-001020. Accident description and EMS: On I-65 North, while on the way to pick up her son in Louisville, a silver car in the left lane swerved into her lane, causing her to lose control and execute a 180-degree spin.
